text: Proneptunea is a genus of sea snails, marine gastropod mollusks in the family Buccinidae, the true whelks. ==Species== Species within the genus Proneptunea include: * Proneptunea rossiana Dell, 1990 * Proneptunea rufa Oliver & Picken, 1984 * Proneptunea subfenestra Oliver & Picken, 1984 ==References== ==External links== * Category:Buccinidae
title: Proneptunea
